Except as lawfully permitted, we do not knowingly collect personal information
from children under these ages for any purpose. If you believe that we have
personal information of a child under these ages without parental/guardian
consent, or if you are the parent or guardian of the user and wish to withdraw
consent, please contact us at
dpo_aov@proximabeta.com
and we will delete such information.
