We Use Your Personal Information
This
section provides more detail on the types of personal information we collect
from you, and why. For users who live in the European Economic Area, United
Kingdom, Switzerland, Brazil or Turkey (“
Relevant Jurisdiction
”), it
also identifies the legal basis under which we process your data
.
Personal Information
Use
