more information on any specific changes to the way we process that personal
information that might differ to this privacy policy prior to collecting or
processing any additional information. In some cases, the information may be shared
with us with your consent – and if that is the case, we will provide you with
further information on how we process that information and your rights. We
generally retain such information for the duration of the relevant activity and
thereafter in accordance with legal obligations.
