     as your GPS information if you use location based services. This
     information is collected directly from you.
Audio and visual
     information such as your social media profile picture, audio messages and
     gameplay video. This information is collected directly from you and from
     social media platforms if you choose to sign up using a social media
     account, or if you choose to share your gameplay.
Other information
     described in subdivision (e) of Section 1798.80, including information
     about your gender. This information is collected directly from you in the
     context of being our consumer.
