Where we use service
providers who might have access to your personal information, we require them
to have privacy and security standards that are comparable to ours. We use
contracts and other measures with our service providers to maintain the
confidentiality and security of your personal information and to prevent it
from being used for any purpose other than as provided in this Privacy Policy.
